Package ohos.ivihardware.cluster.model

Provides abstract classes about cluster control callback and basic data types.

This package is used together with ohos.ivihardware.cluster, providing information about property setting callback, property subscription callback, subscription filter types, and property data structure.

Since:
3
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ClusterActuatorCallback
    A callback class pertaining to setting a Cluster signal of the actuator type.
    ClusterSignalCallback
    A callback class pertaining to subscribing to a specified Cluster signal.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ClusterPropertyInfo
    A wrapper class for Cluster signal values.
    ClusterSubscription

  • Enum Summary

    Enumerates data types of the Cluster signal.
    ClusterPropertyInfo.PropertyType
    Enumerates node types of the Cluster signal.
